# 🍯 Bee-lightful Honey Website

This is the source code for the **Bee-lightful Honey** website — a small-batch honey and seasonal fruit shop powered by bees 🐝.  
It’s built as a static site with [Netlify CMS](https://www.netlifycms.org/), so you can **log in and edit content without coding**.

---

## 🌐 Features
- Static site: fast, simple, and secure.
- Netlify CMS: edit homepage, products, and content through a friendly admin panel.
- Mobile-friendly design.
- Ready for e-commerce expansion (currently “browse only” until payments are enabled).

